  (text "When the TSAL is\non, this MOSFET\nswitch closes. This\ncompletes the ground \npath of the LEDs and\nHV sense PCB."
    (at 207.645 149.225 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid 31f2af45-b6e5-407d-b177-565a9338e8e5)
  )
  (text "When LVMS turns on,\nSR latch is set. The\nlatch can only be \nreset if the LVMS then\nturns off."
    (at 144.78 182.88 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid 324bca1d-2e69-4189-9ad0-0b22dcacc621)
  )
  (text "Optional current limiting\nresistors for LEDs. Can be\nbridged if not needed."
